      "seed": 1368161809,
      "version": 641,
      "versionNonce": 1596774449,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1766672702006,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- its a 2 player game can be extended to have more players\n- Each player takes turn in moving their placement on the 10x10 board (numbered from 0 to 99)\n    by rolling the dice starting from position one (i.e cell 0)\n\nThis game consists of 3 main components\n- Dice -> Yields a random number between 1 to 6 which tell the player to move x number of cells\n    in forward direction\n- Ladders -> Help the player jump to a higher position\n- Snakes -> Steps down the player to the lower position",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- its a 2 player game can be extended to have more players\n- Each player takes turn in moving their placement on the 10x10 board (numbered from 0 to 99)\n    by rolling the dice starting from position one (i.e cell 0)\n\nThis game consists of 3 main components\n- Dice -> Yields a random number between 1 to 6 which tell the player to move x number of cells\n    in forward direction\n- Ladders -> Help the player jump to a higher position\n- Snakes -> Steps down the player to the lower position",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
