      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1766674440353,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Player : \n    Holds variable to save id or Name\n    current_positon on the board\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n2. Dice :\n    Holds Dice Count which tells with howmany dice we are playing the game\n    rollDice() method to simply to find the number between 1 to 6, for N\n          (dice count) times and sum it up",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Player : \n    Holds variable to save id or Name\n    current_positon on the board\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n2. Dice :\n    Holds Dice Count which tells with howmany dice we are playing the game\n    rollDice() method to simply to find the number between 1 to 6, for N\n          (dice count) times and sum it up",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
